@model PartyInvites.Models.GuestResponse
@{
    Layout = null;
}
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Thanks</title>
    <link href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="text-center">
    <p>
        <h1>Thank you, @Model.Name!</h1>
        @if (Model.WillAttend == true)
        {
            @:It's great than you're coming. The drinks are already in the fridge!
        }
        else
        {
            @:Sorry to hear that you can't make it, but thanks for letting us know.
        }

    </p>
    @*С применением атрибута вспомогательной функции дескриптора asp - acti on
    создается URL, который нацелен на метод действия по имени ListResponses ():*@
    Click <a class="nav-link" asp-action="ListResponses">here</a> to see who is coming.
</body>
</html>

